      "id": "listing-task-fields",
      "x": 1120,
      "y": 245,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 390,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "🔑 id (PK)\n📝 task_code (UK) - 任务编码\n🏷️  category_id - 品类ID\n🔗 item_id (FK) - 商品ID\n   ⚠️  发布成功后回填\n🚦 status - 任务状态\n   • 0 = DRAFT 草稿\n   • 10 = Pending Audit 待审核\n   • 11 = Approved 已通过\n   • 20 = Online 已上架\n📦 item_data (JSON) - 完整商品数据\n📋 source_type - 数据来源\n   • merchant_portal\n   • operator_form\n   • supplier_push\n   • batch_import 📌\n🎯 audit_type - 审核类型\n   • skip/auto/manual\n🔄 retry_count - 重试次数\n🔐 version - 乐观锁版本号\n👤 created_by - 创建人\n🕐 created_at",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
