    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "legend-content",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 700,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 165,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "① Excel上传 → 创建batch_task\n② 解析Excel → 每行创建batch_item\n   (task_id=NULL)\n③ 校验通过 → 创建listing_task\n   → 回填batch_item.task_id\n④ 审核通过 → 发布商品\n   → 创建item\n   → 回填listing_task.item_id\n   → 回填batch_item.item_id\n⑤ 更新batch_task统计计数",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "legend"
      ],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1343824713,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772090715314,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aW",
      "angle": 0,
      "frameId": null,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "① Excel上传 → 创建batch_task\n② 解析Excel → 每行创建batch_item\n   (task_id=NULL)\n③ 校验通过 → 创建listing_task\n   → 回填batch_item.task_id\n④ 审核通过 → 发布商品\n   → 创建item\n   → 回填listing_task.item_id\n   → 回填batch_item.item_id\n⑤ 更新batch_task统计计数",
      "autoResize": true
    },
