    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "key-points-content",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 700,
      "width": 340,
      "height": 165,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "✅ batch_item.task_id初始NULL\n   校验失败不创建listing_task\n✅ batch_item.item_id初始NULL\n   发布成功后才回填\n✅ listing_task是核心状态机\n   管理审核、发布全流程\n✅ batch_task只做聚合统计\n   total/success/failed计数\n✅ 三表解耦，职责清晰\n   批次、行、任务分离",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
