      "width": 420,
      "height": 230,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "📅 分表命名规范：\n\nlisting_batch_task_tab_202602\nlisting_batch_item_tab_202602\nlisting_task_tab_202602\n\nlisting_batch_task_tab_202603\nlisting_batch_item_tab_202603\nlisting_task_tab_202603\n\n...\n\n💡 按 created_at 字段月份分表",
