    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "sharding-note-content",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 1295,
      "width": 1340,
      "height": 70,
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "⚠️ 注意事项：\n① item_tab 不需要分表（数据量相对可控，需要全局查询）\n② 跨月批次查询需要 UNION ALL 多个月份的表  ③ 使用数据库中间件（如 ShardingSphere）可简化分表逻辑\n④ 建议保留最近 6-12 个月热数据，更早的数据归档到冷存储（如 S3/OSS）",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#d9480f",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "sharding-note"
      ],
      "roundness": null,
