      "text": "🔑 id (PK)\n🔗 task_id (FK) → listing_task\n🔗 item_id (FK) → item\n🔄 from_status - 原状态\n   0=DRAFT, 10=Pending...\n🔄 to_status - 新状态\n   10=Pending, 11=Approved...\n⚡ action - 触发动作\n   • submit - 提交审核\n   • approve - 审核通过\n   • reject - 审核拒绝\n   • publish - 发布上架\n   • offline - 下架\n💬 reason - 变更原因\n👤 operator_id - 操作人\n🕐 changed_at",
