    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "audit-tables-note-content",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 1890,
      "width": 1340,
      "height": 60,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "① listing_audit_config_tab：全局配置表，不分表，按品类×数据源配置审核策略（跳过/自动/人工/快速通道）\n② listing_audit_log_tab：审核日志表，按月分表，记录审核决策细节（规则引擎结果、审核员意见）\n③ listing_state_history_tab：状态历史表，按月分表，记录任务全生命周期的每次状态变更（DRAFT→Pending→Approved→Online）\n④ 三表协同：config 驱动审核策略 → audit_log 记录审核决策 → state_history 记录状态流转，形成完整审计链路",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#495057",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "audit-note"
      ],
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1,
      "version": 2,
      "versionNonce": 1830421799,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772090715314,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "b09",
      "angle": 0,
      "frameId": null,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "① listing_audit_config_tab：全局配置表，不分表，按品类×数据源配置审核策略（跳过/自动/人工/快速通道）\n② listing_audit_log_tab：审核日志表，按月分表，记录审核决策细节（规则引擎结果、审核员意见）\n③ listing_state_history_tab：状态历史表，按月分表，记录任务全生命周期的每次状态变更（DRAFT→Pending→Approved→Online）\n④ 三表协同：config 驱动审核策略 → audit_log 记录审核决策 → state_history 记录状态流转，形成完整审计链路",
      "autoResize": true
    }
